2
00:00:13,680 --> 00:00:18,515
GODZILLA

3
00:00:22,022 --> 00:00:26,982
Produced by Tomoyuki Tanaka

4
00:00:27,027 --> 00:00:31,987
Screenplay by Takeo Murata
